{"tid":448962,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然身邊好多人 但其實自己係單機嘅","createTime":"2017-10-26T17:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T23:35:50.000Z","uid":2479,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e94fd1310773b50a4bdd33f6cf76d5f49313c69c","tid":448962,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"去到一個地方<br />\n你可以同嗰度嘅人玩得好埋<br />\n但裏面冇一個人係屬於自己 佢地可以組成一個group<br />\n而自己 就喺啲group插嚟插去 <br />\n<br />\n你相識好耐嘅朋友 因為有咗新朋友 慢慢忽略你<br />\n因為新朋友好玩 所以會慢慢咁 唔會點樣理你<br />\n雖然佢冇講到出聲話唔想同你玩 但自己其實feel到<br />\n<br />\n當去到某啲時候 就會發現自己原來係單機嘅一個<br />\n而嗰種feel唔係sad 係唏噓 <br />\n可能都係有唔開心 係自己唔覺得係啫<br />\n<br />\n你以為自己係嗰個圈子？<br />\n其實唔係 嗰個地方係屬於人地 冇自己份"},{"pid":"228b8083fd0b48bd3f7905d8759956c4c10d055a","tid":448962,"uid":100950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"此地不留人自有留人處<br />\n我成日都咁同自己講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fd311daad6bbf0a1630c3282fe198a1b46220b","tid":448962,"uid":17889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:41:22.000Z","msg":"Same feeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6553deb2b344cc35de5be4a99c1c9cd20db5e985","tid":448962,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"當你去到某一個位 你就開始明白<br />\n寧靜 反而係你最需要既<br />\n試下開始接受"},{"pid":"fd08f764defa294b18d3c17e83fe049e05e25d81","tid":448962,"uid":60689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"成日對身邊嘅人覺得好重要 但人地根本對你wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0dec710d3637236f0dbd3e16f41ef44d61e243","tid":448962,"uid":137379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:51:57.000Z","msg":"最無奈既係 成長令自己改變左原有性格，優點<br />\n令到自己再無性格優勢去挽留舊朋友 <br />\n<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fb4f2a23789eac9df277892a751f88